{"tid":680384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「火箭」滅火筒射上四層樓毀冷氣","createTime":"2018-05-27T06:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T12:29:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f14a04a60361aa8000d241b98ad255b0089d576b","tid":680384,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T06:55:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180527/20402743\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180527%2F20402743&d=0gAxxgObGgPCwDOQEb4rKghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=170018e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180527%2F20402743&h=cdc1ebb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180527/20402743</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月27日 <br />\n<br />\n「火箭」滅火筒射上四層樓毀冷氣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180527/large/a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180527%2Flarge%2Fa.jpg&h=e83b42bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■深水埗前晚發生滅火筒突然噴氣一飛沖天，擊中4樓一部冷氣機後跌回地上意外。司徒韋桐攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】深水埗發生滅火筒變火箭毀屋傷人罕見意外！一名拾荒者前晚在街頭撿獲一個滅火筒後，扭開樽蓋擬拎走銅件變賣，滅火筒卻一飛沖天向上噴射60多米撞漽大廈四樓單位外牆冷氣機打碎窗框，再墜地激射火花，一名男途人被碎件擊中後腦受傷。受災女住戶稱冷氣機被撞擊一刻「好似被飛彈射中」，幸屋內無人受傷。警方正尋找涉案拾荒者下落。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180527/large/a0502b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180527%2Flarge%2Fa0502b.gif&h=14a382af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被滅火筒砸中冷氣機單位，窗框凹陷。翁鈺輝攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180527/large/a0502c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180527%2Flarge%2Fa0502c.gif&h=d8098231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■意外中的滅火筒事後跌回地面，被扭開的開關掣亦遺留地上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n墮地時組件彈傷途人<br />\n<br />\n現場為福榮街177號一幢大廈，遭「射擊」單位是四樓李家，他們一家三口居住。現場消息稱，前晚10時許，一名拾荒者在福榮街及欽州街交界街口，拾獲棄置衣車及滅火筒，其時他腳踩滅火筒銅嘴，嘗試扭開取走銅嘴變賣，惟滅火筒樽身突然失控噴氣，朝上噴射60多米，擊中涉事單位外牆的冷氣機，<br />\n撞擊力之猛，令窗框凹陷，窗戶玻璃粉碎，滅火筒再反彈直墮地面，墮地一刻洩射火花，一名男途人當時與墮地滅火筒相當接近，幸未被擊中，當場嚇至轉身走避。另一名55歲姓麥男子在大廈對開行人路走過，則被滅火筒膠組件濺傷後腦，要送院敷治。<br />\n<br />\n■記者司徒韋桐、姜偉康  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n婦飲一口覺鹹帶異味報警　疑尿水侍僱主印傭涉落毒被捕<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n滅火筒擊爆4樓毀冷氣機　住戶：似被飛彈擊中"},{"pid":"d51cfb42bb4686bf394116b28b793edefdf96e27","tid":680384,"uid":63950,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T07:05:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed7037fabf86c94156108c82f0a7b1d68ff8e889","tid":680384,"uid":49974,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"d51cfb42bb4686bf394116b28b793edefdf96e27","tid":680384,"uid":63950,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T07:05:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T07:07:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f7ee1c66aabc6bc1bae9f3c9f9c56acb775748","tid":680384,"uid":42188,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T07:09:04.000Z","msg":"個拾荒者真係低賤"},{"pid":"b041246b8d3650c250eb99762479dbf1d3148905","tid":680384,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T07:09:20.000Z","msg":"民間嘅「小型飛彈」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7276d3f4d46d23aea767769b83927acf1466bed4","tid":680384,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"60f7ee1c66aabc6bc1bae9f3c9f9c56acb775748","tid":680384,"uid":42188,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T07:09:04.000Z","msg":"個拾荒者真係低賤"},"cited